				\begin{document}$$ 3\mathrm{D}\mathrm{P}\mathrm{C}-\mathrm{M}\mathrm{R}\mathrm{A}=\frac{1}{N}{\displaystyle \sum_{t=1}^N}{M}^2(t)*\sqrt{\left({V}_x^2(t)+{V}_y^2(t)+{V}_z^2(t)\right)} $$\end{document}3DPC−MRA=1N∑t=1NM2t*Vx2t+Vy2t+Vz2t

While [6] proposed the following:2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
